description:
Maria Bamford (Netflix's Lady Dynamite, Old Baby) is here and she claims to have no deal breakers. Will she handle the questions Anna and Sim throw her way? On this episode, Anna discusses her parents' reactions to landing her first role in Scary Movie, Maria delivers a sneak peek of what she’ll say in her upcoming college commencement speech, and Jack Pratt makes another special appearance with his favorite movie quote! Later, they call Tiffany, whose husband wants to move to LA and become an actor, and then Liana, whose long term boyfriend bought a wedding ring, but still hasn’t popped the question! Tune in and hang out!
